### Get product by ID (replace with actual ID from creation response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Search all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### Search products with keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=laptop

### Search electronics category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=electronics

### Search by price range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?minPrice=50&maxPrice=500

### Search products in stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?inStock=true

### Search with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=2

### Search with sorting by price descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?sort=price_desc

### Search with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=electronics&minPrice=100&maxPrice=2000&inStock=true&sort=price&page=1&pageSize=10

